Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下十隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是十五隻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得都沒人想接這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(水啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(以吾之名下令)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(回應吾聲)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是想接來當成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一份工作前的過渡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來接下這工作是我失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種森林深處哪會有甚麼村子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼眸的深處照映著我的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容令我感到些許耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四目相對的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便已感受到 I feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如空中出現的\N(那片天空的)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道彩虹一樣\N(彩虹一般)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著七色光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我的內心雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是笑容 又或是傷悲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願分享我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能對我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕猛烈強風 亦或漫長黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你陪伴在我身邊 僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就令我感覺能再踏出下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(青年 與小小女孩相遇)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你在說甚麼 )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我聽不懂)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 既然是魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這裡 來 需要 這個 )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道這個該怎麼講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你要給我嗎 )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是餓壞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說過魔人族的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被折去一隻角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且被族人放逐的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的孩子自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一起被放逐的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(汝 保護 人 一起 存在 )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(拉古說不可以靠近那裡)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(因為那裡有野獸聚集 很危險)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一起存在 否定)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(野獸 拒絕)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你東西吃完就趕快回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(過來)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(拉古就在那一邊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼  前面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(可是拉古說不能靠近那裡)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從角的形狀看來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔人族的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(他說會有野獸聚集)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(所以要離開這裡不能靠近)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是"野獸"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是"否定"嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能待在自己的遺體身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則很快就會有野獸聚過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她恐怕是這個意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽從了他的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這黑暗的森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(不要緊吧 )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見這種狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就無法扔下她不管了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(隸屬於大地之物)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(以吾之名下令)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(化為吾所期望的樣貌)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少先將他安葬起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(埋葬 土 死 人)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就稍微比較像墳墓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法連墓誌銘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做出來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(謝謝你)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是種緣份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回去庫羅茲以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吾名為迪爾)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(汝 名字 )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吾 一起 汝 走 )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好輕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一起用走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽都要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我們要去哪裡 )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點重量不算甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是庫羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北邊是貴族街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南邊是庶民街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們要去的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庶民街就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去驅除魔獸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我工作做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行稅 兩人份的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎和父親死別了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是魔人族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會負責收留她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話應該不會有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上很熱鬧讓你嚇一跳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡在拉邦德國之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是第二大的都市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言不通果然很不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從正門進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會弄得很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天又變得更漂亮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算說這種傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會算得比較便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔 再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸餡餅還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛剛炸好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要從後門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在搞甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情我一會兒再做說明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別講得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到小貓小狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先跟你借一下浴室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先借一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(不要 不要)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要幫你洗澡而已　　(不要 不要)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(快停手 好難為情)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下變得乾淨多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這樣簡直判若兩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你又搞了甚麼麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛滿十八歲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾歲才有這麼大的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在森林中撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是她父親的魔人族死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我小時候的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有點太大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只懂魔人族的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼跟她交談的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為魔人族的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和咒文語是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先調查她的身分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉烏哈．賽格爾．約拿迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小孩是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是迪爾撿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙看起來有點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不會把你吃掉的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有符合條件的人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒找到你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這孩子在一起的魔人族男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設拉提娜是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負重罪的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理說情報應該會無關種族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在阿古達爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言板上才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她這麼小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理說應該也能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出尋人啟事才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那個魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拉提娜的父親了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聞到香味了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(迪爾 我可以吃嗎 )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拿這孩子怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒想過後果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就帶她過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先帶她來城裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再找孤兒院收留嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把語言不通而且
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是其他人種的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給這城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都缺乏經費的孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也不會有甚麼好事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔 快去拿水來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太燙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等明天再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我們要去哪裡 )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這裡的閣樓租下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這邊也是店裡的置物間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂糟糟的就先包涵一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然是累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對語言跟現在的狀況都一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被人帶來這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(廁所 廁所)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要先教她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"廁所"這個單字的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓她再睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會丟下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(否定 問題)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她之前一直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一人待在那種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起得真還早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去洗個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不要動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶拉提娜過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的頭髮真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換做我就不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不提她是魔人族的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷掉的其中一隻角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別太引人注目比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這樣講不對嗎  很奇怪嗎 )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這樣講沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(正確)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經學會怎麼打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個聰明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她第一個打招呼的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇 竟然還有上甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是給你吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯說是為拉提娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子果然很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個肯尼斯竟然會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩這麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直獨自一人待在森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒辦法吃到甜食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自一人是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以後也都會是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去市場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在沒鞋子穿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也鬆垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太可憐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫羅茲數一數二的冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾．雷齊這下也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形象盡失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡放在閣樓的那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許得再找其他地方放了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(迪爾 這裡是甚麼 )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是市場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"購物"該怎麼講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對女孩子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一竅不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處問問總會有辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她交給這城市的孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也不會有甚麼好事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然多少會有一點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考慮到拉提娜的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了不少東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為甚麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果被店員牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你決定好該怎麼辦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有其他選項吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不但是個冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個單身漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會離家好幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段期間可以讓她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在我們店裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也得看迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼下決定囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了戰鬥甚麼都不會的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底能不能養育小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 到底能不能讓她幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要負責照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為拉提娜的監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每過一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的喜歡就增加一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你磨蹭我的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都變得不再重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生在世上的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都敵不過這個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以真希望 明天或者後天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為溺愛中毒丟下工作不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超乎保護過度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛操心的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得我變得異常堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已下定決心要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至能與正義為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is 勇者 but 殘念!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你深深著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜蜜蜜或是卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是傻爸爸的末期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算當個殘念勇者也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你永遠陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到連冒險也無法繼續的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is 勇者 but 殘念